<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>و<span class="c1">"عكل الأمر"</span> و<span class="c1">"أعكل"</span> أي <span class="c2">(١)</span>: أشكل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>و<span class="c1">"عتم الليل"</span> و<span class="c1">"أعتم"</span>: أظلم.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>و<span class="c1">"فلك"</span> في الأمر<span class="c1">" و"</span>أفلك<span class="c1">": لج.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>و"عصفت الريح<span class="c1">" وأعصفت: اشتد هبوبها<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>و"سف <span class="c2">(٢)</span> الخوص<span class="c1">" و"</span>أسفه<span class="c1">": نسجه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>و"غضب القرن<span class="c1">" و"</span>أعضبه<span class="c1">": كسره<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>و"عسر الغريم<span class="c1">" و"</span>أعسره<span class="c1">": طالبه على عسره.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>و"قاله البيع و<span class="c1">"أقاله"</span> و<span class="c1">"حزنه الأمر"</span> و<span class="c1">"أحزنه"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>و<span class="c1">"شغله الأمر"</span> و<span class="c1">"أشغله"</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> و<span class="c1">"فغر فاه"</span> و<span class="c1">"أفغره"</span> فتحه ومن توافق <span class="c1">"فعل"</span> و<span class="c1">"أفعل"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c1">"غطش الليل"</span> و<span class="c1">"أغطش"</span>: أظلم.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>و<span class="c1">"غدرت الليلة"</span> و<span class="c1">"أغدرت"</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>: اشتد ظلامها.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>و<span class="c1">"عوز الشيء"</span> و<span class="c1">"أعوز"</span>: تعذر، وكذلك الرجل إذا افتقر.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) هـ والأصل سقط "أي".<br>(٢) هـ "سفت"<br>(٣) ع "وشغله".<br>(٤) ك "غذرت واغذرت هـ "عذرت وأعذرت".</p> </div>